Package: openbci-core
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, openbci-libmultiplexer0 (>> 0.1.3-4), openbci-multiplexer (>> 0.1.3-4), openbci-multiplexer-python (>> 0.1.3-4), libbluetooth-dev, python-protobuf (>= 2.5), xsel, python-serial, python-pygame, python-scipy, python-numpy, python-sip, python-qt4, python-bluetooth, python-xlib, python-zmq, python-pyaudio, python-pyside.qtcore, python-twisted, python-scientific, python-matplotlib, python-psutil
Description: Framework used to build BCI's and psychological experiments.
 Platform for Brain Computer Interfaces. This software contains tools
 which allow you to build a complete Brain Computer Interface based
 on EEG, and perform some experiments collecting EEG and other
 biomedical data signals.


Package: openbci
Architecture: all
Depends: openbci-core, openbci-amplifiers (>> 1.8.4-2)
Description: Master package containing whole OpenBCI framework.
 Platform for Brain Computer Interfaces. This software contains 
 tools which allow you to build a complete Brain Computer Interface
 based on EEG, and perform some experiments collecting EEG and
 other biomedical data signals.

